6
00:00:13,130 --> 00:00:15,860
That would lead me to
revealing how I escaped,

7
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:18,580
retired early and how you can too.

8
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:20,527
My eyes were really opened
up to the possibilities

9
00:00:20,527 --> 00:00:22,220
to make a mass income.

10
