no one really wanted to talk about money.

13
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:29,670
It was so taboo.

14
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:30,870
Hi guys it's Mark.

15
00:00:30,870 --> 00:00:32,920
So I've got some news for you,

16
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:36,170
retiring with enough money to
enjoy the rest of your life.

17
00:00:36,170 --> 00:00:39,820
Sitting on a beach, sipping
on whatever your heart desires

18
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:42,280
is becoming near enough impossible.

19
